Package: elm
Type: Package
Title: Files Visualizations Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sam Parmar
Maintainer: Sam Parmar <myself@somewhere.net>
Description: Elm is a file visualization tool that allows you to visualize 
  multiple files on your computer in an interactive way. With Elm, you can 
  view your files in a variety of different ways, including by size, file 
  type, and directory tree. Elm makes it easy to gain insights into the files 
  on your computer, helping you to manage your storage more effectively.
